description: 14 September 2012, payment of £200 from Classic Arts Productions, North Kilworth Hall, Green Lane, North Kilworth, Lutterworth, Leicestershire LE17 6HQ, for a guest appearance on Radio 3’s programme ‘Private Passions’.  Hours: 70 mins. (Registered 18 September 2012)
